---
description: RMF control elements <cbuf>, <config>, <exitcfg>, <timeout>
---

### cbuf
Queue a console command after the page is loaded.
```text
<cbuf "exec default">
```

### config
Run a config whenever the page is created or revisited.
```text
<config menus/video>
```

### exitcfg
Run a config whenever a page is destroyed or left.
```text
<exitcfg applysettings>
```

### timeout
Run a command after N seconds.
```text
<timeout 5.0 "menu intro">
```

